# SupportInsight

AI-powered customer support triage dashboard that automatically categorizes support messages and generates professional draft replies.

## Tech Stack

- Frontend: Next.js 15, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, shadcn/ui
- Backend: FastAPI (Python)
- AI: Deepseek API (deepseek-chat model / DeepSeek-V3.2)
- Database: MongoDB Atlas
- Deployment: Vercel (Frontend), Railway (Backend)

## Setup

### Backend Setup

  # Virtual Enviroment

  - cd backend
  - python -m venv venv
  - venv\Scripts\activate

  # Install Dependencies

  - pip install -r requirements.txt

  # Create .env file

  - DEEPSEEK_API_KEY=your_api_key
  - DEEPSEEK_BASE_URL=your_base_url
  - MONGO_URI=your_mongodb_uri
  - MONGO_DB=your_db_name

  # Run Application

  - uvicorn main:app --reload

### Frontend Setup
  - cd frontend
  - npm install
  - npm run dev